data.meta_description: TECHTRON CORPORATE LLP is a Limited Liability Partnership (LLP) based in the state of Maharashtra with the LLP Identification Number (LLPIN) ABZ-7019. The company was founded on 2-Jan-2023, and is registered under the Registrar of Companies (RoC) Mumbai. The primary activity of the company is focused on Retail sale via e-commerce. The LLP has an obligation of contribution of Rs. 100000. The registered office of the company is located at 47/001, GIRNAR SHANTI NAGAR CHS LTD SHANTI NAGAR, SECTOR NO 01, MIRA ROAD - EAST Thane Thane Maharashtra-401107. data.text:
At Quid Connect, our passion lies in facilitating connections between Indian exporters and the right buyers for their products, by providing a platform that is seamless, efficient and easy to use. Our platform allows exporters to showcase their products to a global audience, while enabling buyers to find the products they need with ease. With a team of experts who are well-versed in the intricacies of exporting, we are committed to providing excellent customer service to both exporters and buyers. When you choose Quid Connect, you can trust that you are reaching the right audience and maximizing your business's potential.

Quid Connect is a part of Quid Solutions, a company that has dedicated itself to providing comprehensive services to Indian exporters. Our team of experts at Quid Solutions is committed to helping our clients get their registration work related to export done, and we can also connect exporters with custom house agents to ensure that the exporting process is smooth and hassle-free. In addition, we offer selling services to our premium members, which allows them to expand their business and reach a wider audience. At Quid Solutions and Quid Connect, we are dedicated to helping Indian exporters succeed, and we are constantly striving to provide the best possible service to all of our clients.

In conclusion, whether you are a seasoned exporter or just starting out, Quid Connect and Quid Solutions are here to help you take your exporting business to the next level. Join us today and experience the benefits of our platform for yourself!
